Package org.shikha.eviction

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EvictionKeyHandle
    This is used to handle the Eviction key as per specific implementation.
    EvictionStrategy<K>
    This interface needs to be implemented to provide Eviction Strategy.
    EvictionStrategyFactory
    This factory interface needs to implement to create the specific instance of Eviction Strategy.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LRUEvictionStrategy<K>
    LRUEvictionStrategy is used to evict the least recently keys.
    LRUEvictionStrategyFactory
    Factory class to provide the instance of LRU Eviction Strategy.
